commit_message_format.template:
fix: upgrade {package} to {version} for CVE-{ID}

- Addresses CVE-{ID} in {package}
- Upgraded from {old-version} to {new-version}
- Concert recommendation: {recommendation-details}
- Resolves #{issue-number}

pr_description_template.template:
## CVE Remediation

**CVE ID:** CVE-{CVE-ID}
**Package:** {package}
**Severity:** {severity}

## Changes

- Upgraded {package} from {old-version} to {new-version}
- Applied Concert recommendation: {recommendation-details}

## Concert Analysis

{concert-vulnerability-details}

## Testing

CI/CD will validate this change. Unit test failures and code compatibility issues will be addressed in a separate workflow.

## References

- Resolves #{issue-number}
- Concert Application: {application-name}
- Concert Recommendation ID: {recommendation-id}

completion_message_format.template:
✅ CVE remediation complete:
- Created PR #{pr_number}: {pr_title}
- PR URL: {html_url}
- Branch: {branch_name}
- Package: {package} upgraded from {old_version} to {new_version}
- Resolves issue #{issue_number}
